2 Highlight the desired custom set- tings bank and press MENU/OK.EDIT/SAVE CUSTOM SETTING AF CUSTOM 1 · ASSIGNED MF CUSTOM 2 � ASSIGNED CUSTOM 3 � ASSIGNED ↓ CUSTOM 4 � ASSIGNED BACK EXIT
